<spush><font:Arial:20>The Mine Launcher a.k.a. Bubblegun<spop>

<bitmap:share/misc/help/wpn_gl.png>The Mine Launcher can fire up to four mines in quick succession. Firing it doesn't drain power away from a CAT's armor but instead draws from the same ammo source as the grenades. Once in position, the mines work like a B.O.U.N.C.E. that's triggered by nearby enemies.
